<paragraph id="4BA1BF2AAB51E9FD0FF191D3772373A9" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Terrestrial, evergreen, under shrubs in damp places mixed forests, on rocks, soil banks. Alt. 2650-3200 m.</paragraph>
